data.description: Welcome home! Don't miss out on this beauty located in Simpsonville, SC! This well maintained move-in ready gem is located in the sought after Morning Mist community. This lovely home features 3 bedrooms, 2.5 bathrooms, 2,381 sqft, plus a large bonus room with a closet. This bonus room can be converted into a 4th bedroom, a family playroom, or used as an office or workout room. The options are limitless! Home is located in a private and quiet cul-de-sac within the community. Upon entering the home, you will step into the foyer. To the left, there is a formal dining room and a formal living room located to the right. This room could be converted into an office or closed off. There is an open floor plan with a nice sized great room that features a fireplace. The gourmet kitchen features plenty of cabinet and counter space, as well as stainless steel appliances. There is a breakfast nook that features a small island and chairs. This island offers additional cabinet space, but can also be replaced if chosen, as it is not built in. Upstairs, you will find a spacious owner's suite, two guest suites, and the bonus room. The owners suite features a trey ceiling and nice size walk-in closet. The owner's bath features a double vanity, garden tub, and stand-alone shower. There is a patio out back with a large backyard that is fenced in and well-maintained. Plus, a shed for extra storage! The attached 2-car garage is already finished. Newer roof and water heater. HVAC is 1 year old.  Community has a pool area and covered table area that is perfect for summer time! Located within close proximity to I-385, restaurants, shopping, parks, and more!   In Addition: This home features solar panels. Panels will be paid in full by the Seller at closing. As a new owner, you will reap all of the benefits & energy savings, at NO COST to you!   Don't miss this opportunity to own this lovely home in the popular Morning Mist community. Schedule your showing today!
